\v 1 \x * \xo 12:1 \xt Ro 7:21; 1Ko 9:24-25; Hi 10:36\x*M…®t in kerek hi nepei hetpiyem h…®r n…®paa nises h…®m me God werek werek h…®r yap…®rwe nerp wit ke God n…®rai n…®re m…®t nerp n…®r n…®kerek h…®r nesiuken neit skul. Te haiu m…®t emweik…®n sip emwet menmen yap…®rwe mamraiwaank o menmen enum kerek haiu hanhan emisesim emr…®akem te h…®ram em…®t. Haiu emnaiw…®rem mar ke m…®t…®k kesiuknen kewenwo laplap h…®rak kenepim kew…®rem te h…®rak kesiuken waswas. Haiu emnaiw…®rem em…®t te haiu emises menmen werek werek God kehim…®tenai haiu emisesim.
